column8: Cloudy. Very high (80%) chance of rain. Winds east to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h turning north to northeasterly in the evening.

Mostly cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers, becoming less likely during the afternoon. The chance of a thunderstorm in the morning and afternoon. Some moderate falls possible across the outer eastern suburbs. Winds north to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h shifting cooler southwesterly 20 to 30 km/h in the middle of the day.
Cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers, most likely in the morning and afternoon. Winds south to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h becoming light in the evening.
Patchy morning fog in the east. Partly cloudy day. Slight (30%) chance of a shower. Light winds becoming southerly 15 to 20 km/h during the day then becoming light during the evening.
Patchy morning fog. Mostly sunny afternoon. Light winds becoming southeast to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h during the afternoon then becoming light during the evening.
Patchy morning fog. Partly cloudy day. Slight (30%) chance of a shower. Light winds becoming south to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h during the day.
Partly cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers. Light winds becoming northeast to southeasterly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning.
Partly cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers. Winds north to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h shifting south to southeasterly 25 to 35 km/h during the day.
